## Video drivers/hardware acceleration. Please avoid translating 'OpenGL' and 'ANGLE'.

preferences-video-driver = Videodrivrutin
preferences-video-driver-opengl-mac = OpenGL (rekommenderas på Mac)
preferences-video-driver-software-mac = Mjukvarurendering (rekommenderas ej)
preferences-video-driver-opengl-other = OpenGL (snabbare, kan orsaka problem)
preferences-video-driver-software-other = Mjukvarurendering (långsammare)
preferences-video-driver-angle = ANGLE (kan fungera bättre än OpenGL)
preferences-video-driver-default = förval
